model

Class TableModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
      • model.TableModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, javax.swing.table.TableModel

    public class TableModel
extends javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
    Extension of AbstractTableModel class. Contains references to TableSchema with information on table columns, the parent TableModel and the GUI representation Table. TableModel holds all table rows in form of Record objects and query conditions and condition values applicable to this table in HashMap objects.
    Author:
    Milan Radeta

        public TableModel(TreeNode node,
          Table table,
          TableModel parentTableModel)
        TableModel constructor. Gets column names and codes from provided TreeNode that represents the database table using PreparedStatement objects. Acquires all rows from the database table the node represents. Alerts the user if the table does not exist in the database.
